---
title: Easy Beef Burger & Creamy Pesto Dressing with Parmesan Kumara Fries
description: Tomato sauce is always classic on a burger, but this time we've swapped it out for one of our other favourite classics; creamy pesto dressing. Served with Parmesan-coated kumara fries, you'll be thanking us all night for this easy and mouth-watering meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-burger-creamy-pesto-dressing-a72a4cf7.jpg
